---
const photo = "/images/imgcompleta/img_completa-8.jpg";
---

<section
  class="w-full py-20 relative overflow-hidden"
  style="background-image: url('/images/bg-paper.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <img
      src="/images/png-decore-9.png"
      alt=""
      class="absolute top-8 right-6 w-24 sm:w-32 lg:w-40"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/png-decore-8.png"
      alt=""
      class="absolute bottom-20 right-28 w-24 sm:w-32 lg:w-[200px] rotate-[-70deg] origin-bottom-right"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative">
    <h2 class="text-center text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b4a9b]">
      En México, solo 11 refugios protegen a niñas y niños
      <span class="text-[#f0559f]"> sobrevivientes de trata.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src={photo}
          alt="Niña"
          class="w-full max-w-xl mx-auto rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5">
        <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#2b4a9b]">
          ¡DOS <span class="text-[#f0559f]">NUEVOS</span>
          <br />
          <span class="text-[#f0559f]">REFUGIOS</span>!
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700">
          Queremos construir <strong class="text-[#2b4a9b]">dos refugios especializados</strong>
          que representen hogar, seguridad y futuro.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700">
          Y además construir el <strong class="text-[#2b4a9b]">primer refugio</strong>
          especializado en varones víctimas de este delito.
        </p>
        <button
          class="bg-[#f0559f] hover:bg-[#e14d8a] text-white font-semibold py-3 px-10 rounded-full text-sm sm:text-base uppercase tracking-wider transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
        >
          Dona aquí
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
